== SDK MIGRATION (NEW - 2026-02-15)
================================================================================

Goal: Reduce ~56% code duplication across 94 plugins/handlers by adding an SDK
layer. Expected reduction: ~21,650 lines (68% overall).

Charter: docs/SDK_PROJECT_CHARTER.md
Full Plan: .claude/plans/frolicking-shimmying-comet.md

## Phase 1: Stabilize IPC Contract [DONE - 2026-02-15]
[X] Create plugins/ipc/PROTOCOL.md (document message envelope)
[X] Create plugins/ipc/testdata/ golden fixtures
    [X] detect request/response JSON
    [X] ingest request/response JSON
    [X] enumerate request/response JSON
    [X] extract-ir request/response JSON
    [X] emit-native request/response JSON
[X] Create plugins/ipc/testutil/ normalization helpers
[X] Document error envelope rules (stable codes, retryable vs non-retryable)

## Phase 2: Create SDK Package [DONE - 2026-02-15]
[X] Create plugins/sdk/runtime/ (dispatch, lifecycle)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/format/ (FormatConfig, Run)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/tool/ (ToolConfig, Run)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/ir/ (corpus read/write, hashing)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/blob/ (store, artifact IDs)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/errors/ (standardized errors, codes)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/types/ (IPC type re-exports)
[X] Create plugins/sdk/README.md with examples
